title: Dimitra Tsiliaskopoulos
text:
Dimitra Tsiliaskopoulos, better known as Dimi Poulos is an Australian <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Goalkeeper%20%28association%20football%29">goalkeeper</a> who last played for <a href="Western%20Sydney%20Wanderers%20FC%20W-League">Western Sydney Wanderers</a> in the <a href="W-League%20%28Australia%29">W-League</a>, as an injury replacement for <a href="Young%20Matildas">Young Matildas</a> goalkeeper <a href="Mackenzie%20Arnold">Mackenzie Arnold</a>.
She has also played in the American <a href="USL%20W-League">W-League</a> and the <a href="Primera%20Divisi%C3%B3n%20%28women%29">Spanish league</a>.
